{"tid":603736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【偷垃圾桶搭港鐵】阿伯屋企凌亂堆滿雜物 友人：偷垃圾桶冇乜嘢嘅　","createTime":"2018-03-24T04:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T10:01:21.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f77342b3d81366411c26970de976f41610ef3f1","tid":603736,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"69歲姓袁伯伯因涉嫌偷垃圾桶，並帶著垃圾桶乘搭港鐵列車，昨日被警方拘捕，並於昨晚被押返黃大仙的寓所搜證。記者今早去到袁伯的寓所，門外走廊泊有一架手推車，大門破爛殘舊，但袁伯不在家中，屋內只有袁伯一名姓陳朋友應門。<br />\n<br />\n袁伯的寓所堆滿雜物，污穢不堪，並傳出陣陣異味，屋內有水無電。姓陳男子表示，與袁伯相識多年，自己為區內街坊，因知袁伯出事，所以到其家中幫手，據他所知，袁伯並無家人，單位只有袁伯一個人居住，又指袁伯有領取綜援。陳男對於袁伯涉嫌偷垃圾桶，認為「冇乜嘢嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n有同層女街坊則表示不認識袁伯：「我噚晚返嚟先見到拉佢，唔識呢個人，應該搬嚟冇幾耐。」<br />\n<br />\n同層姓鄭女童則指，平日有見袁伯穿著清潔工人制服，行動舉止正常，認為「偷垃圾桶做得唔啱」， 覺得袁伯推垃圾桶搭港鐵更是匪夷所思。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180324/57988825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57988825&d=h6VOf%2BDcfMswPncNcCHfFQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=1d335186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57988825&h=c123f121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180324/57988825</a><br />\n<br />\n明明偷野唔啱  睇FB因為係老人家偷就轉晒風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc06960b9fc6f6c2e8430c43b47c8723771c31a","tid":603736,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeaf81f3a4e5907dbbd2388e84767420038e883","tid":603736,"uid":110207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"依D癈老真係唔快D死無用<br />\n<br />\n第一偷野犯法<br />\n<br />\n第二自私 俾你換左個垃圾筒, 本身做清潔果個呀姐點算?<br />\n<br />\n第三無諗過其他人感受 成卡地鐵陪你臭 整到污糟邋遢<br />\n<br />\n利伸住公屋見唔少依D人"},{"pid":"f22244a8ccb844870bfcf7504e8d6528c1a26106","tid":603736,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"平日有見袁伯穿著清潔工人制服<br />\n<br />\n做清潔做上腦定鐘意cosplay清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26e6dae82290ebf91b7e13ca581c55826418ffc","tid":603736,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f22244a8ccb844870bfcf7504e8d6528c1a26106","tid":603736,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"平日有見袁伯穿著清潔工人制服<br />\n<br />\n做清潔做上腦定鐘意cosplay清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"著清潔工人制服方便執垃圾<br />\n同著反光衣睇concert一樣原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58e58e5acbe302fd7007aa4a58f96bd19f91d6b","tid":603736,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"老毒撚日常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafd2309486305ff91b8958cce3b9bc2d0732523","tid":603736,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26e6dae82290ebf91b7e13ca581c55826418ffc","tid":603736,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f22244a8ccb844870bfcf7504e8d6528c1a26106","tid":603736,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"平日有見袁伯穿著清潔工人制服<br />\n<br />\n做清潔做上腦定鐘意cosplay清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"著清潔工人制服方便執垃圾<br />\n同著反光衣睇concert一樣原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08